{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"ce0040cd0ceb63ee76fdd1","title":"P36 长按二维码页：固件版本号显示开发记录","desc":"","updated":1780371367057,"created":1780371330025,"custom":{},"fname":"开发记录.2026-05-14_P36二维码页固件版本号显示开发记录","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"0019c37475f246ab9afa5420bbbebce0","links":[{"from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":3,"offset":538},"end":{"line":25,"column":41,"offset":576},"indent":[]},"value":"开发记录.2026-05-14_P36二维码页固件版本号显示开发记录"}],"anchors":{"p36-长按二维码页固件版本号显示开发记录":{"type":"header","text":"P36 长按二维码页：固件版本号显示开发记录","value":"p36-长按二维码页固件版本号显示开发记录","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"1-背景":{"type":"header","text":"1. 背景","value":"1-背景","line":16,"column":0,"depth":2},"2-改动文件清单":{"type":"header","text":"2. 改动文件清单","value":"2-改动文件清单","line":23,"column":0,"depth":2},"3-详细改动":{"type":"header","text":"3. 详细改动","value":"3-详细改动","line":33,"column":0,"depth":2},"31-mqtt_backend_clienth--暴露版本宏":{"type":"header","text":"3.1 mqtt_backend_client.h — 暴露版本宏","value":"31-mqtt_backend_clienth--暴露版本宏","line":35,"column":0,"depth":3},"32-mqtt_backend_clientc--移除重复宏":{"type":"header","text":"3.2 mqtt_backend_client.c — 移除重复宏","value":"32-mqtt_backend_clientc--移除重复宏","line":44,"column":0,"depth":3},"33-lv_example_meterc--版本标签实现":{"type":"header","text":"3.3 lv_example_meter.c — 版本标签实现","value":"33-lv_example_meterc--版本标签实现","line":48,"column":0,"depth":3},"331-头文件包含":{"type":"header","text":"3.3.1 头文件包含","value":"331-头文件包含","line":50,"column":0,"depth":4},"332-新增静态变量":{"type":"header","text":"3.3.2 新增静态变量","value":"332-新增静态变量","line":54,"column":0,"depth":4},"333-标签创建ui_build_base_layers":{"type":"header","text":"3.3.3 标签创建（ui_build_base_layers）","value":"333-标签创建ui_build_base_layers","line":62,"column":0,"depth":4},"334-显示逻辑second_desktop_refresh_center--ui_result_qr_static-分支":{"type":"header","text":"3.3.4 显示逻辑（second_desktop_refresh_center — UI_RESULT_QR_STATIC 分支）","value":"334-显示逻辑second_desktop_refresh_center--ui_result_qr_static-分支","line":75,"column":0,"depth":4},"335-层级处理":{"type":"header","text":"3.3.5 层级处理","value":"335-层级处理","line":99,"column":0,"depth":4},"336-清理与空指针检查":{"type":"header","text":"3.3.6 清理与空指针检查","value":"336-清理与空指针检查","line":104,"column":0,"depth":4},"4-未改动项":{"type":"header","text":"4. 未改动项","value":"4-未改动项","line":111,"column":0,"depth":2},"5-效果":{"type":"header","text":"5. 效果","value":"5-效果","line":119,"column":0,"depth":2},"6-注意事项":{"type":"header","text":"6. 注意事项","value":"6-注意事项","line":140,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"w0x0z2descd3ztesnx5y6au","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"p36-长按二维码页固件版本号显示开发记录\">P36 长按二维码页：固件版本号显示开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#p36-长按二维码页固件版本号显示开发记录\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"p36-长按二维码页固件版本号显示开发记录-1\">P36 长按二维码页：固件版本号显示开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#p36-长按二维码页固件版本号显示开发记录-1\"></a></h1>\n<p><strong>日期</strong>：2026-05-14<br>\n<strong>工程</strong>：<code>bk7252n_sdk-SDK_3.0.76.1_witch_lcd</code><br>\n<strong>编译命令</strong>：<code>scons --beken=bk7252n -j4</code></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-背景\">1. 背景<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-背景\"></a></h2>\n<p>P36 按键长按后进入静态二维码页面，此前仅显示 <strong>SN（设备序列号）</strong> + <strong>二维码图片</strong> + <strong>底部下载提示</strong>。<br>\n为便于现场排查固件版本，需要在 SN 下方显示当前应用版本号，即 <code>MQTT_OTA_CURRENT_VERSION</code> 宏的值（<code>V0.0.1</code>）。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-改动文件清单\">2. 改动文件清单<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2-改动文件清单\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>文件</th><th>改动类型</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/mqtt_backend_client.h</code></td><td>新增宏</td><td>暴露 <code>MQTT_OTA_CURRENT_VERSION</code> 供 UI 层引用</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/mqtt_backend_client.c</code></td><td>删除宏</td><td>移除本地定义，统一从 header 获取</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/pages/lv_example_meter.c</code></td><td>修改</td><td>新增版本标签 <code>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl</code> 及配套逻辑</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-详细改动\">3. 详细改动<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#3-详细改动\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"31-mqtt_backend_clienth--暴露版本宏\">3.1 <code>mqtt_backend_client.h</code> — 暴露版本宏<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#31-mqtt_backend_clienth--暴露版本宏\"></a></h3>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token comment\">/** 当前应用固件版本号，用于 OTA 检查及界面展示 */</span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">MQTT_OTA_CURRENT_VERSION</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"V0.0.1\"</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>置于 <code>#ifndef __MQTT_BACKEND_CLIENT_H__</code> 之后、<code>typedef struct</code> 之前，供 <code>mqtt_backend_client.c</code> 和 <code>lv_example_meter.c</code> 共用。</p>\n<h3 id=\"32-mqtt_backend_clientc--移除重复宏\">3.2 <code>mqtt_backend_client.c</code> — 移除重复宏<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#32-mqtt_backend_clientc--移除重复宏\"></a></h3>\n<p>删除原有的本地 <code>#define MQTT_OTA_CURRENT_VERSION \"V0.0.1\"</code>，改为从 header 继承，避免版本号分散在两处导致不一致。</p>\n<h3 id=\"33-lv_example_meterc--版本标签实现\">3.3 <code>lv_example_meter.c</code> — 版本标签实现<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#33-lv_example_meterc--版本标签实现\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"331-头文件包含\">3.3.1 头文件包含<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#331-头文件包含\"></a></h4>\n<p><code>mqtt_backend/mqtt_backend_client.h</code> 改为无条件包含（原先仅在 <code>LV_DESKTOP_STATUS_WIFI_USE_MQTT=1</code> 时包含），确保 <code>MQTT_OTA_CURRENT_VERSION</code> 宏始终可用。</p>\n<h4 id=\"332-新增静态变量\">3.3.2 新增静态变量<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#332-新增静态变量\"></a></h4>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">lv_obj_t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>与 <code>s_sec_qr_sn_lbl</code> 同级声明。</p>\n<h4 id=\"333-标签创建ui_build_base_layers\">3.3.3 标签创建（<code>ui_build_base_layers</code>）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#333-标签创建ui_build_base_layers\"></a></h4>\n<p>在 <code>s_sec_qr_sn_lbl</code> 创建之后、<code>s_sec_qr_img</code> 之前：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\">s_sec_qr_ver_lbl <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">lv_label_create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_sec_qr_panel<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">lv_label_set_long_mode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> LV_LABEL_LONG_DOT<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_set_style_pad_all</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_add_flag</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> LV_OBJ_FLAG_HIDDEN<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>标签作为 <code>s_sec_qr_panel</code> 的子对象，初始隐藏。</p>\n<h4 id=\"334-显示逻辑second_desktop_refresh_center--ui_result_qr_static-分支\">3.3.4 显示逻辑（<code>second_desktop_refresh_center</code> — <code>UI_RESULT_QR_STATIC</code> 分支）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#334-显示逻辑second_desktop_refresh_center--ui_result_qr_static-分支\"></a></h4>\n<p>在 SN 标签显示后、二维码图片显示前：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* 版本号：紧贴 SN 下方，不改变原有面板尺寸与二维码位置 */</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">lv_label_set_text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Ver: \"</span> MQTT_OTA_CURRENT_VERSION<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_set_style_text_font</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> LV_FONT_DEFAULT<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_set_style_text_color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">lv_color_hex</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0x606060</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_set_style_text_align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> LV_TEXT_ALIGN_CENTER<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">lv_label_set_long_mode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> LV_LABEL_LONG_DOT<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_set_width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> THERMAL_QR_FRAME_W <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_set_height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> LV_SIZE_CONTENT<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> LV_ALIGN_TOP_MID<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n             THERMAL_QR_SN_Y_OFS <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> THERMAL_QR_SN_ROW_H <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_clear_flag</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> LV_OBJ_FLAG_HIDDEN<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>关键参数：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>字体</strong>：<code>LV_FONT_DEFAULT</code>（与 SN 行一致）</li>\n<li><strong>颜色</strong>：<code>#606060</code>（灰色，比 SN 的 <code>#101010</code> 浅，形成层级区分）</li>\n<li><strong>高度</strong>：<code>LV_SIZE_CONTENT</code>（自适应内容，不额外占用固定像素）</li>\n<li><strong>Y 偏移</strong>：<code>THERMAL_QR_SN_Y_OFS + THERMAL_QR_SN_ROW_H - 4</code> = <code>3 + 24 - 4 = 23</code>，即 SN 行底部向上 4 像素，使版本号紧贴 SN 但不占用额外间距</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"335-层级处理\">3.3.5 层级处理<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#335-层级处理\"></a></h4>\n<p>二维码图片（<code>s_sec_qr_img</code>）创建在版本标签之后，LVGL 中后创建的子对象绘制在上层，会遮挡版本文字。<br>\n在二维码显示后调用 <code>lv_obj_move_foreground(s_sec_qr_ver_lbl)</code> 将版本标签提到最顶层，确保文字可见。</p>\n<h4 id=\"336-清理与空指针检查\">3.3.6 清理与空指针检查<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#336-清理与空指针检查\"></a></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>清理函数中新增 <code>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl = NULL</code></li>\n<li><code>second_desktop_refresh_center</code> 空指针检查新增 <code>s_sec_qr_ver_lbl == NULL</code></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"4-未改动项\">4. 未改动项<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#4-未改动项\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code>thermal_happy_lv.h</code></strong>：不新增布局常量，不调整 <code>THERMAL_QR_FRAME_H</code>。版本号使用 <code>LV_SIZE_CONTENT</code> 高度，叠在 SN 与二维码之间的自然空隙，不改变面板尺寸。</li>\n<li><strong>二维码图片位置</strong>：<code>THERMAL_QR_SN_Y_OFS + THERMAL_QR_SN_ROW_H + THERMAL_QR_PREVIEW_TOP_PAD</code> 保持不变。</li>\n<li><strong>SN 行样式与位置</strong>：完全不变。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"5-效果\">5. 效果<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#5-效果\"></a></h2>\n<p>长按 P36 进入二维码页面后，显示布局（自上而下）：</p>\n<pre><code>┌──────────────────────┐\n│     SN: xxxxxxxx     │  ← 深色 #101010, Y=3, H=24\n│   Ver: V0.0.1        │  ← 灰色 #606060, Y=23, 自适应高度\n├──────────────────────┤\n│                      │\n│     [ 二维码 ]       │  ← 120×120, Y=27（位置未变）\n│                      │\n├──────────────────────┤\n│   扫码下载 APP ...   │  ← 底部提示\n└──────────────────────┘\n</code></pre>\n<p>版本号在 SN 正下方、二维码上方，不改变面板外框尺寸和原有各元素位置。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"6-注意事项\">6. 注意事项<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#6-注意事项\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>版本号字符串来源为 <code>MQTT_OTA_CURRENT_VERSION</code> 宏，OTA 检查上报和 UI 展示共用同一处定义，后续发版时只需修改 <code>mqtt_backend_client.h</code> 中一处即可。</li>\n<li>版本标签使用 <code>LV_SIZE_CONTENT</code> 高度，若后续版本号字符串变长（如 <code>V1.0.0-beta</code>），标签会自动扩展高度，无需调整布局常量。</li>\n<li>如版本文字与二维码顶部重叠过多，可微调 Y 偏移中的 <code>-4</code> 值（增大负数上移，减小负数下移）。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/\">root</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"BK7252N AI 打印机固件文档库","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"e5d7823b7368b844c5d7bde821080751","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"开发记录.项目开发记录总纲","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":83},"end":{"line":8,"column":20,"offset":100},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"开发记录.项目开发记录总纲"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"开发记录.项目交接资料","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":3,"offset":115},"end":{"line":9,"column":18,"offset":130},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"开发记录.项目交接资料"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"阶段性开发总结","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":3,"offset":145},"end":{"line":10,"column":14,"offset":156},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"阶段性开发总结"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"tutorial","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":3,"offset":169},"end":{"line":11,"column":15,"offset":181},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"tutorial"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"开发记录.2026-05-01_0234-AI打印机固件开发记录","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":3,"offset":219},"end":{"line":17,"column":39,"offset":255},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"开发记录.2026-05-01_0234-AI打印机固件开发记录"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"开发记录.2026-05-03_热敏打印与MQTT开发记录","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":3,"offset":258},"end":{"line":18,"column":36,"offset":291},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"开发记录.2026-05-03_热敏打印与MQTT开发记录"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fn